<h4 id="toc0"><span>你可能也喜欢：</span></h4>
<p><a href="/scp-2959">SCP-2959</a> - 我们都做了什么，我们都干了什么by<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kinchtheknifeblade" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1345012); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1345012&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1602954829" alt="kinchtheknifeblade" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1345012)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kinchtheknifeblade" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1345012); return false;">kinchtheknifeblade</a></span></p>
<blockquote>
<p>SCP-2959是对一群实体的统称，受影响基金会人员将其称为“D级人员”。</p>
</blockquote>
<p><a href="/scp-2559">SCP-2559</a> - “我听说有事情发生了”by<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rimple" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2320004); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2320004&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1602954829" alt="Rimple" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2320004)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rimple" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2320004); return false;">Rimple</a></span></p>
<blockquote>
<p>SCP-2559是一种致命的病毒感染和认知危害：相信自己被SCP-2559感染的人在所有情况下都会被感染。</p>
</blockquote>
<p><a href="/scp-2076">SCP-2076</a> - “自射可提高子弹抵抗力” <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/logan-armstrong" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1720957); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1720957&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1602954829" alt="Logan Armstrong" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1720957)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/logan-armstrong" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1720957); return false;">Logan Armstrong</a></span></p>
<blockquote>
<p>任何受SCP-2076影响的智能存在会表现出对将此信息危害所述内容付诸生活实践的持续性兴趣，并伴有一种将此种行为当作日常活动向外介绍的长期欲望。受影响者均会对此种行动带来的不良后果视而不见。</p>
